SELECT
    <%=sourceSystem%> || '::' || "FscmTopModelAM_WorkOrderAM_WorkOrderPVO"."WorkOrderPEOWorkOrderId"     AS "ID",
    CAST("FscmTopModelAM_WorkOrderAM_WorkOrderPVO"."WorkOrderPEOCreationDate" AS TIMESTAMP)              AS "CreationTime",
    "FscmTopModelAM_WorkOrderAM_WorkOrderPVO"."WorkOrderPEOActualStartDate"                              AS "StartTime",
    "FscmTopModelAM_WorkOrderAM_WorkOrderPVO"."WorkOrderPEOActualCompletionDate"                         AS "FinishTime",
    "FscmTopModelAM_WorkOrderAM_WorkOrderPVO"."WorkOrderPEOPlannedStartDate"                             AS "ScheduledStartTime",
    "FscmTopModelAM_WorkOrderAM_WorkOrderPVO"."WorkOrderPEOPlannedCompletionDate"                        AS "ScheduledFinishTime",
    "FscmTopModelAM_WorkOrderAM_WorkOrderPVO"."WorkOrderPEOPlannedStartQuantity"                         AS "OrderItemQuantity",
    "DistinctItem"."ItemBasePEOPrimaryUomCode"                                                           AS "QuantityUnit",
    "FscmTopModelAM_WorkOrderAM_WorkOrderPVO"."WorkOrderPEOScrappedQuantity"                             AS "ScrapQuantity",
    "FscmTopModelAM_WorkOrderAM_WorkOrderPVO"."WorkOrderPEOCompletedQuantity"                            AS "ProductionQuantity",
    "FscmTopModelAM_WorkOrderAM_WorkOrderPVO"."WorkOrderPEOCompletedQuantity"                            AS "GoodsReceiptQuantity",
    <%=sourceSystem%> || '::' ||"FscmTopModelAM_WorkOrderAM_WorkOrderPVO"."WorkOrderPEOOrganizationId" 
    || '::'  || COALESCE("FscmTopModelAM_WorkOrderAM_WorkOrderPVO"."WorkOrderPEOInventoryItemId", '')    AS "MaterialMasterPlant",
    CAST("FscmTopModelAM_WorkOrderAM_WorkOrderPVO"."WorkOrderPEOWorkOrderNumber" AS VARCHAR(255))        AS "ProductionOrderNumber",
    CASE
        WHEN "FscmTopModelAM_WorkOrderAM_WorkOrderPVO"."WorkOrderPEOWorkOrderStatusId" = '10000' THEN
            TRUE  -- 10000 CANCELED
        ELSE
            FALSE
    END                                                                                                  AS "IsDeleted",
    CASE
        WHEN "FscmTopModelAM_WorkOrderAM_WorkOrderPVO"."WorkOrderPEOWorkOrderStatusId" = '10002' THEN
            TRUE   --10002 COMPLETED
        ELSE
           FALSE
    END                                                                                                  AS "IsDeliveryCompleted",
    <%=sourceSystem%>                                                                                    AS "SourceSystemInstance" 
FROM "FscmTopModelAM_WorkOrderAM_WorkOrderPVO" AS "FscmTopModelAM_WorkOrderAM_WorkOrderPVO"
    LEFT JOIN "FscmTopModelAM_ScmExtractAM_EgpBiccExtractAM_ItemExtractPVO" AS "DistinctItem"
           ON "FscmTopModelAM_WorkOrderAM_WorkOrderPVO"."WorkOrderPEOInventoryItemId" = "DistinctItem"."ItemBasePEOInventoryItemId"
           AND  "FscmTopModelAM_WorkOrderAM_WorkOrderPVO"."WorkOrderPEOOrganizationId" = "DistinctItem"."ItemBasePEOInventoryOrganizationId"
WHERE "DistinctItem"."ItemBasePEOInventoryItemId" IS NOT NULL

SELECT <%=sourceSystem%> || '::' || CAST("WIP_DISCRETE_JOBS"."WIP_ENTITY_ID" AS VARCHAR(255))    AS "ID",
       CAST("WIP_DISCRETE_JOBS"."CREATION_DATE" AS TIMESTAMP)                                    AS "CreationTime",
       "WIP_DISCRETE_JOBS"."NET_QUANTITY"                                                        AS "ProductionQuantity",
       "MTL_SYSTEM_ITEMS_B"."PRIMARY_UOM_CODE"                                                   AS "QuantityUnit",
       "WIP_DISCRETE_JOBS"."QUANTITY_COMPLETED"                                                  AS "GoodsReceiptQuantity",
        <%=sourceSystem%> || '::' || "WIP_DISCRETE_JOBS"."ORGANIZATION_ID" 
        || '::' || COALESCE("WIP_DISCRETE_JOBS"."PRIMARY_ITEM_ID",'')                            AS "MaterialMasterPlant",
       CAST("WIP_DISCRETE_JOBS"."QUANTITY_SCRAPPED" AS FLOAT)                                    AS "ScrapQuantity",
       "WIP_DISCRETE_JOBS"."SCHEDULED_START_DATE"                                                AS "ScheduledStartTime",
       "WIP_DISCRETE_JOBS"."SCHEDULED_COMPLETION_DATE"                                           AS "ScheduledFinishTime",
       "WIP_DISCRETE_JOBS"."ACTUAL_START_DATE"                                                   AS "StartTime",
       "WIP_DISCRETE_JOBS"."DATE_COMPLETED"                                                      AS "FinishTime",
       CAST("WIP_ENTITIES"."WIP_ENTITY_NAME" AS VARCHAR(255))                                    AS "ProductionOrderNumber",
       CASE
           WHEN "WIP_DISCRETE_JOBS"."STATUS_TYPE" = '7' THEN TRUE
           ELSE FALSE
           END                                                                                   AS "IsDeleted",
       CASE
           WHEN "WIP_DISCRETE_JOBS"."STATUS_TYPE" = '4' THEN TRUE
           ELSE FALSE
           END                                                                                   AS "IsDeliveryCompleted",
           <%=sourceSystem%>                                                                     AS "SourceSystemInstance"
FROM "WIP_DISCRETE_JOBS" AS "WIP_DISCRETE_JOBS"
   INNER JOIN "MTL_SYSTEM_ITEMS_B" AS "MTL_SYSTEM_ITEMS_B"
      ON "WIP_DISCRETE_JOBS"."PRIMARY_ITEM_ID" = "MTL_SYSTEM_ITEMS_B"."INVENTORY_ITEM_ID"
         AND "WIP_DISCRETE_JOBS"."ORGANIZATION_ID" = "MTL_SYSTEM_ITEMS_B"."ORGANIZATION_ID"
   LEFT JOIN "WIP_ENTITIES" AS "WIP_ENTITIES"
      ON "WIP_DISCRETE_JOBS"."WIP_ENTITY_ID" = "WIP_ENTITIES"."WIP_ENTITY_ID"
WHERE NULLIF(CAST("MTL_SYSTEM_ITEMS_B"."INVENTORY_ITEM_ID" AS VARCHAR(255)), '') IS NOT NULL

SELECT <%=sourceSystem%> || '::' || "AFPO"."MANDT" || '::' || "AFPO"."AUFNR" || '::' || "AFPO"."POSNR"                  AS "ID",
    CAST("AFPO"."ETRMP" AS TIMESTAMP)                                                                                   AS "CreationTime",
    "AFPO"."PSMNG"                                                                                                      AS "ProductionQuantity",
    "AFPO"."MEINS"                                                                                                      AS "QuantityUnit",
    "AFPO"."WEMNG"                                                                                                      AS "GoodsReceiptQuantity",
	<%=sourceSystem%> || '::' || "AFPO"."MANDT" || '::' || "AFPO"."MATNR" || '::' || "AFPO"."DWERK"                     AS "MaterialMasterPlant",
    <%=sourceSystem%> || '::' || "AFPO"."MANDT"                                                                         AS "SourceSystemInstance",
    CAST("AFPO"."AUFNR" AS VARCHAR(255))                                                                                AS "ProductionOrderNumber",
    CASE WHEN NULLIF("AFPO"."XLOEK", '') IS NULL THEN FALSE ELSE TRUE END                                               AS "IsDeleted",
    CASE WHEN NULLIF("AFPO"."ELIKZ", '') IS NULL THEN FALSE ELSE TRUE END                                               AS "IsDeliveryCompleted",
    CAST("AFPO"."PSAMG" AS FLOAT)                                                                                       AS "ScrapQuantity",
    CAST("AFKO"."GSTRS" AS DATE) + CAST(TIMESTAMPDIFF(SECOND, CAST("AFKO"."GSUZS" AS DATE),
                    "AFKO"."GSUZS") AS INTERVAL SECOND)                                                                 AS "ScheduledStartTime",
    CAST("AFKO"."GLTRS" AS DATE) + CAST(TIMESTAMPDIFF(SECOND, CAST("AFKO"."GLUZS" AS DATE),
                    "AFKO"."GLUZS") AS INTERVAL SECOND)                                                                 AS "ScheduledFinishTime",
    CAST("AFKO"."GSTRI" AS DATE) + CAST(TIMESTAMPDIFF(SECOND, CAST("AFKO"."GSUZI" AS DATE),
                    "AFKO"."GSUZI") AS INTERVAL SECOND)                                                                 AS "StartTime",
    CAST("AFKO"."GLTRI" AS DATE) + CAST(TIMESTAMPDIFF(SECOND, CAST("AFKO"."GEUZI" AS DATE),
                    "AFKO"."GEUZI") AS INTERVAL SECOND)                                                                 AS "FinishTime"
FROM "AFPO" AS "AFPO"
    LEFT JOIN "AFKO" AS "AFKO"
        ON "AFKO"."MANDT" = "AFPO"."MANDT"
            AND "AFKO"."AUFNR" = "AFPO"."AUFNR"
    LEFT JOIN "AUFK" AS "AUFK"
        ON "AFPO"."MANDT" = "AUFK"."MANDT"
            AND "AFPO"."AUFNR" = "AUFK"."AUFNR"
WHERE NULLIF("AFPO"."MANDT", '') IS NOT NULL
  AND "AUFK"."AUTYP" IN ('10')
